This is what we did while staying at @bonnie.bln ‘s place in one of the most dopest neighborhoods in Berlin-Kreuzberg at Kottbusser Tor:

After enjoying a Berlin original burgers place called @burgermeister.official we were heading up to the biggest hippie park in the world which is the former Berlin airport #tempelhoferfeld 🛫 ..just image skating on an airfield, this felt so unreal😱
